name: Vintage gold star earings
description:
Funky vintage gold earings for pierced ears. 

These cute star design earings are bang on trend and one of a kind... for the girl who wants something a little more unique...

Size 2.5cm x 2.5cm aprox

name: Vintage 'Kiss' earings
description:
Cute love heart shaped earings with filigree boy kissing girl within. 

These vintage sweeties will be sure to get you attention - one of a kind and gold they are quirky and charming in equal measure.

Swing style earing with aprox 2cm drop

name: Vintage Cameo Necklace
description:
Stunning vintage necklace.

It's long length and chunky chain gives it a modern look and the pendant is of ample proportion to sit perfectly with any funky outfit. With beautiful cameo engraved detail, her delicate hair and features are trully a work of art.

This is one of a kind so if you like it, act fast!

Chain length 30cm 
Pendant 3.5cm x 2cm

name: Vintage 3 chain necklace
description:
This vintage goodie just oozes charm and style! 

With 3 rows of chains, each one a different style, and featuring a cute little love heart detail you'd be crazy not to snap up this little lovely... what's more it's the only one there is!

Sits perfectly around the neck and is length adjustable, making it look great with all sort of tops and dresses, especially boob tubes.

Approximate Length from side to side 45cm (including length of adjuster)

This is vintage with attitude!

name: Vintage 'Lady' Necklace
description:
Gorgeous vintage long length necklace. Fabulously funky design features the torso of a beautiful woman. Gilt plated, antique silver colour.

Think Alexa Chung and Kelly Osbourne, this necklace would update any drab outfit needing a touch of vintage-bling!

Only one of it's kind so want it = get it!

Aprox length of chain 35cm
Pendant aprox 4.5cm x 4.5cm
